{"tid":1434391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人抗爭策略 - 呢兩日就係心態既備戰期！","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T18:32:21.000Z","uid":276303,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb37c207d49be731a12c567ef470dc0bc9fcffa1","tid":1434391,"uid":276303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:23:46.000Z","msg":"堅決拒絕大台<br />\n群龍無首天下大利。五大訴求既然缺一不可，則不存在談判，更無須搭建大台派遣代表。<br />\n<br />\n堅決拒絕形式主義<br />\n各有各做，行之有效就支持，行禮如儀則棄之。要抗擊港共政權拉一派打一派策略，應該立即宣佈運動再不存在和理非與勇武兩派，從此只有抗暴派，光復香港時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n堅決拒絕割蓆<br />\n香港命運共同體，放核彈都要攬！"},{"pid":"93fb1e6d11f48c55f49dc3bf730974ef7e0a47bd","tid":1434391,"uid":179402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=66668077\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=6a8f5e2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi